<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AA2D32F5FEB3FA27" bold="true" box="[126,259,1453,1477]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">Distribution</emphasis>
. –
</emphasis>
<collectingCountry id="34FF764B274E1205AB7B32F6FE24FA27" box="[296,404,1454,1477]" name="Singapore" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">Singapore</collectingCountry>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="04F26550274E1205AA2D32B5FE2DF8E7" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="4C5736DB274E1205AA2D32B5FE2DF8E7" blockId="7.[126,765,1517,1797]" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AA2D32B5FF4CF9E7" bold="true" box="[126,252,1517,1541]" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AA2D32B5FF50F9E7" bold="true" box="[126,224,1517,1541]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">Remarks</emphasis>
. –
</emphasis>
Although 
<taxonomicName id="8BE84D58274E1205AB2032B6FDA1F9E7" authority="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert, 2008" authorityName="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2008" box="[371,529,1518,1541]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Hercostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lanceolatus" status="new species">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AB2032B6FDA1F9E7" box="[371,529,1518,1541]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">H. lanceolatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="65AF57B2274E1205A87332B6FD16F9E7" box="[544,678,1518,1541]" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
, is very closely related to 
<taxonomicName id="8BE84D58274E1205AB6B3156FE19F9C7" authority="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert, 2008" authorityName="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2008" box="[312,425,1550,1573]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Hercostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="limosus" status="new species">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AB6B3156FE19F9C7" box="[312,425,1550,1573]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">H. limosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="65AF57B2274E1205ABE53156FD89F9C7" box="[438,569,1550,1573]" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
, we consider them as a distinct species. 
<taxonomicName id="8BE84D58274E1205AB3D3176FDBFF9A7" authorityName="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2008" box="[366,527,1582,1605]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Hercostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lanceolatus">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AB3D3176FDBFF9A7" box="[366,527,1582,1605]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">H. lanceolatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is much smaller, the stigma is lanceolate and longer and the denticle on the aedeagus is smaller and more basad in position. 
<taxonomicName id="8BE84D58274E1205A8DA3136FD4CF967" authorityName="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2008" box="[649,764,1646,1669]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Hercostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="limosus">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205A8DA3136FD4CF967" box="[649,764,1646,1669]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">H. limosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is larger, has a shorter and wider stigma and a stronger denticle on the aedeagus, that is closer to the tip of the aedeagus. For a comparison with 
<taxonomicName id="8BE84D58274E1205AB1F3196FDE4F907" authority="Becker, 1922" authorityName="Becker" authorityYear="1922" box="[332,596,1742,1765]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Hercostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="notatus">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AB1F3196FE0CF907" box="[332,444,1742,1765]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">H. notatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="28794B2A274E1205AB903196FDE4F907" author="Becker, T" box="[451,596,1742,1765]" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" pagination="1 - 247" refId="ref7585" refString="Becker, T. H., 1922. Dipterologische Studien Dolichopodidae der Indo-Australischen Region. Capita Zoologica, 1: 1 - 247." type="journal article" year="1922">Becker, 1922</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, we refer to the remarks under 
<taxonomicName id="8BE84D58274E1205AB7131B6FE25F8E7" authorityName="Zhang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2008" box="[290,405,1774,1797]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Hercostomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="24" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="limosus">
<emphasis id="7E9CEAC9274E1205AB7131B6FE25F8E7" box="[290,405,1774,1797]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="24">H. limosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
